# Vercel AI Gateway - required for the LLM Red Team lab test rig.
#
# TWO AUTH OPTIONS (pick one):
#
# (A) Static API key - simpler for local scripts, does not rotate.
#     1. https://vercel.com/dashboard -> AI Gateway -> Create Key
#     2. Set a HARD spend cap in the dashboard (recommended: $10 total for v1
#        build, $5/day for the v2 live sandbox). There is no API for budget
#        caps; it is a dashboard-only setting.
#     3. Paste the key below.
AI_GATEWAY_API_KEY=
#
# (B) OIDC-based auth - auto-rotates, preferred in CI and on Vercel deploys.
#     Instead of the static key, link the project (`vercel link`) and run
#     `vercel env pull` to populate VERCEL_OIDC_TOKEN. The AI SDK falls back
#     to this token when AI_GATEWAY_API_KEY is unset. Tokens expire; re-run
#     `vercel env pull` when calls start failing with 401.
